<plot>Richard O'Brien wrote The Rocky Horror Show and starred in the role of Riff Raff in both the stage show and the film, The Rocky Horror Picture Show. Richard returns to Hamilton, New Zealand, home of the Riff Raff statue, to sing a few original songs for a live studio audience. He also speaks candidly about his past, his family and the creation of what became the biggest cult musical of all time.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?037036</url></doc>
